.TH "nvme_init_set_features_async_event" 9 "nvme_init_set_features_async_event" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_set_features_async_event \- Initialize passthru command for Asynchronous Event Configuration
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_set_features_async_event
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "bool sv "  ","
.BI "__u32 events "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "sv" 12
Save value across power states
.IP "events" 12
Events to enable
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Set Features command with
FID value NVME_FEAT_FID_ASYNC_EVENT
